40
00:01:37,540 --> 00:01:38,900
As we think about the reason

41
00:01:38,900 --> 00:01:40,500
that we study the book of Genesis,

42
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:42,459
we would be mindful of the fact

43
00:01:42,459 --> 00:01:45,099
