53
00:02:10,179 --> 00:02:12,740
If you do not have an understanding,

54
00:02:12,740 --> 00:02:16,279
a proper understanding of this foundational truth

55
00:02:16,279 --> 00:02:18,220
that is given to us in the book of Genesis,

56
