58
00:02:23,740 --> 00:02:27,139
And so we find that this book, the book of Genesis,

59
00:02:27,139 --> 00:02:29,380
is foundational in nature,

60
00:02:29,380 --> 00:02:32,259
and it is foundational for the rest of Scripture.

61
00:02:32,259 --> 00:02:37,179
And I cannot overemphasize that truth this evening.

62
00:02:37,179 --> 00:02:42,020
