80
00:03:34,220 --> 00:03:36,979
But if you understand the foundation of the book of Genesis

81
00:03:36,979 --> 00:03:39,380
and you see even in this first chapter,

82
00:03:39,380 --> 00:03:41,220
Genesis chapter number one,

