85
00:03:46,419 --> 00:03:48,660
and on at least 30 occasions,

86
00:03:48,660 --> 00:03:52,339
the name God or the reference to God is given.

87
00:03:52,339 --> 00:03:55,580
Can you understand why Satan would wanna attack

88
00:03:55,580 --> 00:03:58,660
the truth that is found in Genesis chapter number one

