00:04:01,339 --> 00:04:05,419
And we find that this attack is really being intensified.

91
00:04:05,419 --> 00:04:09,619
We find that it is those that would oppose the truth,

92
00:04:09,619 --> 00:04:13,380
the teaching of creation and the origin of man

93
00:04:13,380 --> 00:04:16,739
and all that is contained, the record of the flood

94
00:04:16,739 --> 00:04:19,260
as it's given beginning in Genesis chapter number six,

95
00:04:19,260 --> 00:04:23,380
we find that the attack is intensifying

96
00:04:23,380 --> 00:04:25,899
in these the last days.

97
00:04:25,899 --> 00:04:27,899
And so therefore, it is imperative

98
00:04:27,899 --> 00:04:30,100
that we as the people of God,

99
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:32,500
that we study the word of God

100
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:34,859
