101
00:04:34,859 --> 00:04:38,700
that we have the foundation for our Christian faith.

102
00:04:38,700 --> 00:04:39,980
Now, the reality this evening

103
00:04:39,980 --> 00:04:42,399
is that we have been instructed in the New Testament

104
00:04:42,399 --> 00:04:44,140
that we're to be students of the word of God,

105
00:04:44,140 --> 00:04:46,420
study to show thyself approved unto God,

106
00:04:46,420 --> 00:04:48,339
a workman that needeth not to be ashamed,

107
00:04:48,339 --> 00:04:51,260
rightly dividing the word of truth.

108
00:04:51,260 --> 00:04:54,279
And so we find that we have been given the responsibility

109
00:04:54,279 --> 00:04:57,260
