00:05:15,980 --> 00:05:18,779
all the things concerning himself

118
00:05:18,779 --> 00:05:22,000
and how foundational the book of Genesis is.

119
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,380
So we understand the importance

120
00:05:23,380 --> 00:05:25,100
of studying the book of Genesis.

121
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:28,500
We need to be able to stand up and give an answer.

