that the man of God might be perfect,

144
00:06:28,179 --> 00:06:30,339
throughly furnished unto all good works.

145
00:06:30,339 --> 00:06:35,179
And we find that the word of God, Genesis is God breathed.

146
00:06:35,179 --> 00:06:36,720
It is God's word.

147
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:38,779
Often we look at the human penman and we say, okay,

148
00:06:38,779 --> 00:06:41,940
