154
00:06:53,579 --> 00:06:56,640
especially in the first 11 chapters.

155
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:58,339
It's God's word.

156
00:06:58,339 --> 00:06:59,179
Amen?

157
00:06:59,179 --> 00:07:03,500
It is God's word and we must stand upon that.

158
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:06,859
The reality is that this evening there are some

159
00:07:06,859 --> 00:07:11,100
