175
00:08:01,019 --> 00:08:02,579
Does it make sense?

176
00:08:02,579 --> 00:08:03,859
And this is the problem.

177
00:08:03,859 --> 00:08:05,579
This is the road by which we go down

178
00:08:05,579 --> 00:08:08,779
