193
00:08:48,059 --> 00:08:50,859
He's saying, listen, the enemy is undermining

194
00:08:50,859 --> 00:08:52,340
the authority of the word of God,

195
00:08:52,340 --> 00:08:54,739
specifically the account of creation,

196
00:08:54,739 --> 00:08:57,580
the creation of the world, the creation of man,

197
00:08:57,580 --> 00:08:59,900
the fall of man, the flood, so on and so forth.

198
00:08:59,900 --> 00:09:01,820
And he's undermining all of that

199
00:09:01,820 --> 00:09:04,099
and he's saying that can't be trusted

200
00:09:04,099 --> 00:09:06,419
