211
00:09:37,059 --> 00:09:39,219
and we have no need for a savior.

212
00:09:40,219 --> 00:09:43,140
But that is contrary to what God's word teaches

213
00:09:43,140 --> 00:09:45,140
and I'm thankful that God created,

214
00:09:45,140 --> 00:09:48,380
he is the creator, he is the sustainer of life

215
00:09:48,380 --> 00:09:49,580
but I'm thankful this evening

216
00:09:49,580 --> 00:09:53,739
