00:10:11,419 --> 00:10:13,019
that's before us this evening,

225
00:10:13,019 --> 00:10:16,459
we understand that as we grasp the knowledge

226
00:10:16,459 --> 00:10:18,179
that is given to us in this book

227
00:10:18,179 --> 00:10:21,019
