231
00:10:27,279 --> 00:10:30,399
it would encourage us to continue to walk with God.

232
00:10:31,399 --> 00:10:33,939
And this evening, as we look at this passage of scripture,

233
00:10:33,939 --> 00:10:37,979
Genesis 1.1, it's only 10 words in our English Bible.

234
00:10:39,159 --> 00:10:40,299
10 words.

235
