But if you consider the 10 words of Genesis 1.1

236
00:10:45,119 --> 00:10:49,599
and you think of the depth and power of these words,

237
00:10:49,599 --> 00:10:53,959
it is almost beyond our human comprehension.

238
00:10:53,959 --> 00:10:58,239
The Bible begins in Genesis 1.1,

239
00:10:58,239 --> 00:11:03,239
in the beginning, God created the heaven and the earth.

240
00:11:05,239 --> 00:11:06,679
I mean, it's amazing.

241
00:11:06,679 --> 00:11:09,519
That's how the Bible begins.

242
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:12,399
You understand this evening that this verse of scripture,

243
00:11:12,399 --> 00:11:14,699
it provides us with a summary statement

244
00:11:14,699 --> 00:11:16,359
of God's creative work.

245
00:11:16,359 --> 00:11:20,319
In the beginning, God created the heaven and the earth.

246
00:11:20,319 --> 00:11:21,839
Beginning in verse number two

247
00:11:21,839 --> 00:11:23,759
and following through the end of the chapter

248
00:11:24,559 --> 00:11:26,279
and into chapter number two, more details are given,

249
00:11:26,279 --> 00:11:28,459
but we find that the work of creation

250
00:11:28,459 --> 00:11:30,399
