253
00:11:34,559 --> 00:11:37,599
and what he created on which day and so on and so forth.

254
00:11:37,599 --> 00:11:39,819
And we find that, but the Bible begins

255
00:11:39,819 --> 00:11:42,319
with these 10 powerful words,

256
00:11:42,319 --> 00:11:47,319
in the beginning, God created the heaven and the earth.

257
00:11:47,839 --> 00:11:49,839
Now it's important for us to note this evening

258
00:11:49,839 --> 00:11:52,919
